data.description: A rarely found almost 1,500 Sq Ft four-bedroom twin featuring two full bathrooms, with an additional two half bathrooms, a finished basement, and outdoor space. The charming brick and stone facade of the home represents the classic style of Delaware County twin homes with modern luxurious living inside. This home underwent a major update in 2020 with new electric, HVAC, appliances, and finishes. The seller is offering a Home Warranty with an acceptable offer.   The open-concept first floor with living room, dining room, and kitchen complete with shaker cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, Center Island, soft-closing drawers, and a decorative backslash. The kitchen provides access to a backyard that extends around to the front of the home, making outdoor entertaining easy.  The second floor is highlighted by a master suite with generous natural light and ample closet space. An additional bedroom featuring plenty of windows for great natural light and a large closet. The third floor offers two more bedrooms with bonus space and a half bathroom. The finished basement offers plenty of storage and an additional bonus space. Great backyard for all of your outdoor entertaining.   With shopping, entertainment, and public transportation with quick access to Baltimore Ave the home is within minutes of Acme Markets, Home Depot, Petco, and Planet Fitness in addition to local favorites Rose Bar & Kitchen and Olympic Diner.  With a Walk Score of 81, this location is highly accessible, enabling you to complete most errands with ease.  The location is ideal, offering close proximity to shopping, restaurants, and all public transportation; just a 20-minute ride to Center City Philadelphia and the Philadelphia International Airport. Appreciate the city's architecture right here in the suburbs.  We are offering a downpayment assistance program: $5,000 in closing costs, $500 for appraisal, and $500 for Home Warranty through Motto Mortgage Expert Solutions.    The property qualifies for the CRA program for a conventional loan with a 3% down payment and no mortgage insurance.
